168
00:07:20.399 --> 00:07:26.196  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Making this sandwich was a lot of work.

169
00:07:26.280 --> 00:07:28.240  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Uh, I'm afraid I know the answer,

170
00:07:28.323 --> 00:07:30.117  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
but have you ever had a job?

171
00:07:30.200 --> 00:07:33.245  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
