172
00:07:33.328 --> 00:07:35.247  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[whispers] Horse.

173
00:07:38.375 --> 00:07:40.627  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
