197
00:08:48.487 --> 00:08:50.947  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Let's just call it a hunch.

198
00:08:51.031 --> 00:08:53.241  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[cha-ching]

