00:09:00.748 --> 00:09:02.250  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Nothing.

201
00:09:02.334 --> 00:09:05.962  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Came in here,
and it was already like this.

202
00:09:06.046 --> 00:09:08.131  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
So where is that award
that is rightfully mine?

203
00:09:08.215 --> 00:09:12.427  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Around my neck--
I mean in a safety deposit box.

204
00:09:12.511 --> 00:09:14.637  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Master Richie,
how come none of the students

205
00:09:14.721 --> 00:09:16.348  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
