00:09:42.207 --> 00:09:46.669  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
This beats memorizing facts
with Extra Homework Girl!"

216
00:09:46.753 --> 00:09:49.714  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Well, I'm sure river rafting
really helped prepare them

