00:10:28.295 --> 00:10:29.504  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[chuckles]

231
00:10:29.588 --> 00:10:31.965  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Not too shabby, huh?

