242
00:10:59.117 --> 00:11:01.369  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Recently I've been losing
clients to my main competitor,

243
00:11:01.453 --> 00:11:04.956  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Saul "The Human Adding Machine"
Rubinstein.

244
00:11:05.039 --> 00:11:07.167  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
