281
00:12:49.269 --> 00:12:50.937  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Nice try, Darcy.

282
00:12:51.020 --> 00:12:52.939  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
