304
00:13:44.823 --> 00:13:46.909  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
so shouldn't you be off shopping with them

305
00:13:46.993 --> 00:13:49.746  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
