308
00:13:56.085 --> 00:13:57.337  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Me.

309
00:13:57.420 --> 00:13:58.463  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
And who was right?

310
00:13:58.546 --> 00:14:00.298  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
- You.
- Mm.

311
00:14:00.381 --> 00:14:02.467  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Good talk. Now get out.

312
00:14:02.550 --> 00:14:04.927  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
