313
00:14:05.011 --> 00:14:06.513  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Why would I help you?

314
00:14:06.596 --> 00:14:08.847  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Once again, you swooped in
with your money,

315
00:14:08.931 --> 00:14:11.142  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
stole my award,
and the sliver of recognition

316
00:14:11.225 --> 00:14:12.727  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I was finally going to receive.

317
00:14:12.811 --> 00:14:14.061  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Look, I was trying to follow your advice

318
00:14:14.145 --> 00:14:15.396  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
and give back.

319
00:14:15.480 --> 00:14:16.690  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I thought I could do that with gifts

320
00:14:16.773 --> 00:14:19.693  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
and trips and vaccinations,

321
00:14:19.776 --> 00:14:21.277  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
you know, for the trips.

322
00:14:21.361 --> 00:14:24.823  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Where were you taking those kids?

323
00:14:24.905 --> 00:14:26.825  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Look, the point is, they needed someone

324
00:14:26.907 --> 00:14:28.159  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
to inspire them.

325
00:14:28.242 --> 00:14:29.536  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
They needed you.

326
00:14:29.619 --> 00:14:31.287  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
