00:14:32.706 --> 00:14:33.665  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Come again?

329
00:14:33.748 --> 00:14:36.751  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
You.

330
00:14:36.835 --> 00:14:40.087  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
