331
00:14:40.171 --> 00:14:43.132  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Don't do it for me. Do it for them.

332
00:14:43.216 --> 00:14:45.760  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Well, as someone else
whose future was destroyed

333
00:14:45.844 --> 00:14:47.011  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
