334
00:14:47.094 --> 00:14:49.389  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I do feel for them.

335
00:14:49.472 --> 00:14:51.224  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
All right, I'll help.

336
00:14:51.307 --> 00:14:53.142  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
