00:15:21.504 --> 00:15:24.799  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Darn it!

350
00:15:24.883 --> 00:15:27.552  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
I came to tell you guys
