352
00:15:29.554 --> 00:15:31.472  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Ooh la la.

353
00:15:31.556 --> 00:15:33.808  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
